@startuml LogsViewLayer Workflow

!theme crt-amber

title LogsViewLayer - Code Flow and Actions

participant "Application" as app
participant "LogsViewLayer" as logs
participant "TDispatcher" as dispatch
participant "AppState" as state
participant "IFluxionLogsPlugin" as plugin

== Initialization ==
app -> logs: AddLayer<LogsViewLayer>(app, z_index)
logs -> logs: OnAdd()
logs -> state: Get application state
state --> logs: Current state
logs --> app: Layer added

== Render Loop ==
app -> logs: OnIterate()
logs -> dispatch: Process action queue
alt UpdateVisibleLogs action
  dispatch -> logs: Call action handler
  logs -> state: Update visible logs chunk
  note right of logs
    Contains Range indices
    for visible log rows
  end note
  state --> logs: State updated
end
logs --> app: Iteration done

app -> logs: OnRender()
alt is_active == true
  logs -> logs: RenderLogsTable()
  
  logs -> state: Get visible logs chunk
  state --> logs: VisibleLogsChunk {logs}
  
  logs -> state: Get table header
  state --> logs: Column definitions
  
  loop For each visible LogRow
    logs -> logs: Render row with columns
    note right of logs
      Display filter colors
      Highlight colors
      Log data
    end note
  end
  
  logs --> app: Logs table rendered
else is_active == false
  logs --> app: Layer hidden
end

== Scrolling & Range Updates ==
note right of logs
  User scrolls table
  Visible range changes
  Dispatcher pushes action
end note

logs -> dispatch: Push UpdateVisibleLogs action
dispatch -> plugin: RequestLogsForRanges()
plugin --> dispatch: LogRow data returned
dispatch -> state: VisibleLogsChunk updated

== Toggle Visibility ==
app -> logs: SetIsActive(true/false)
logs -> state: Mark layer active/inactive
state --> logs: State updated

== Cleanup ==
app -> logs: OnRemove()
logs --> app: Cleanup complete

@enduml
